♫ When the wind sings ♫

534
01:00:34,830 --> 01:00:37,840
[Jirisan]

535
01:00:37,840 --> 01:00:39,568
He came back to the mountain.

536
01:00:39,568 --> 01:00:42,697
And suddenly people started dying.

537
01:00:42,697 --> 01:00:44,682
She's still on the mountain like Yi Kang said.

538
01:00:44,682 --> 01:00:46,617
- Lee Da Won!
- Da Won!

539
01:00:46,617 --> 01:00:47,952
Still no answer from the commander?

540
01:00:47,952 --> 01:00:49,536
Please check this...

541
01:00:49,536 --> 01:00:52,271
We found a pink cell phone. It's covered in blood.

542
01:00:52,271 --> 01:00:54,124
Did she go missing trying to find that?

543
01:00:54,124 --> 01:00:56,627
Why did Da Won record that conversation?

544
01:00:56,627 --> 01:01:00,303
When you're stranded, you panic and do illogical things.

545
01:01:00,303 --> 01:01:02,825
He said it wasn't him this time.

546
01:01:02,825 --> 01:01:05,360
You shouldn't have come back.

547
01:01:06,340 --> 01:01:13,170
♫ It's all I ever wanted. Wished you'd stay— ♫
